Package: ggsh
Type: Package
Title: Jalali Date/Time Scales for 'ggplot2'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Mohsen", "Mollayi", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), email = "mmollayi@gmail.com")
Description: A `ggplot2` extension that enables date/time scales based on Jalali calendar.
    `ggsh` uses classes provided by the `shide` package for mapping aesthetics to date/time types.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/mmollayi/ggsh
BugReports: https://github.com/mmollayi/ggsh/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
